<p class="font-body-sm text-body-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed italic opacity-70">
            A dense exploration of heavy-textured industrial synths and deep-frequency modular patterns. Designed for nocturnal focus and sonic submersion.
          </p>
</div>
